0race.%20Someone%20is%20holding%20up%20the%20French%20flag%2C%20and%20the%20barricades%20read%20%26quot%3BParis%202024.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b11145393cd3c8629b57e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222598%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Olympics%20really%20do%20bring%20people%20together.%3Cp%3EAgnes%20Groonwald%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20articulate%20how%20the%20Olympic%20Games%20bring%20people%20together%20until%20you've%20experienced%20it%20yourself.%20The%20high%20level%20of%20country%20pride%20was%20alive%20and%20well%20inside%20each%20arena%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20see%20anyone%20cross%20the%20line%20for%20those%20allegiances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20there%20was%20an%20air%20of%20inclusivity%2C%20with%20flags%20worn%20as%20capes%20and%20faces%20covered%20in%20paint.%20Attending%20the%20events%20felt%20overwhelmingly%20positive%2C%20even%20when%20our%20team%20didn't%20make%20the%20cut%20%E2%80%A6%20or%20the%20podium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20spectators%2C%20everyone%20employed%20at%20the%20Olympics%20was%20pleasant.%20The%20staff%20outside%20each%20venue%20made%20it%20easy%20for%20us%20to%20find%20our%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20stadiums%2C%20it%20was%20almost%20as%20if%20they'd%20employed%20people%20to%20hype%20up%20the%20crowd%20and%20get%20everyone%20on%20their%20feet%20during%20big%20moments.%20We%20didn't%20need%20much%20of%20that%2C%20though.%20Being%20there%20was%20enough%20to%20get%20us%20excited%20and%20invested%20in%20what%20was%20happening%20around%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Games%20aren't%20even%20over%20yet%2C%20and%20I've%20already%20registered%20for%20tickets%20to%20attend%20the%20next%20Winter%20Games.%20We're%20coming%2C%20Milano%20Cortina%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-surprises-at