ash-ghai-calls-shah-rukh-khan-good-actor-reveals-an-interesting-fact-about-great-actors-amitabh-bachchan-and-dilip-kumar%2Farticleshow%2F112317362.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Red%20Carpet%20Or%20Not%3F%20Furious%20Debate%20Over%20India's%20Olympics%20Uniform%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20contingent's%20attire%20at%20the%20Olympics%20opening%20ceremony%20has%20provoked%20severe%20criticism.%20%26quot%3BEyesore%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Buninspiring%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Bwork%20of%20absolute%20mediocrity%26quot%3B%20-%20the%20feedback%20was%20brutal%20and%20unsparing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sight%20of%20participants%20in%20uniforms%20that%20celebrate%20their%20heritage%20and%20flag%20is%20usually%20the%20most%20electrifying%20part%20of%20the%20opening%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20costumes%20of%20the%20300-member%20Indian%20squad%20and%20officials%2C%20created%20by%20top%20designer%20Tarun%20Tahiliani%2C%20left%20many%20disappointed.%20The%20ikat-inspired%20uniforms%20featured%20men%20in%20kurta-pyjamas%20and%20women%20in%20saris%20in%20the%20colours%20of%20the%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20missed%20the%20chance%2C%20said%20critics%2C%20to%20display%20the%20best%20of%20India%20on%20a%20global%20platform%20and%20showcasing%20authentic%20Indian%20craftsmanship.%20This%20also%20added%20to%20the%20wider%20debate%20on%20how%20India's%20national%20uniform%20should%20reflect%20the%20country's%20rich%20cultural%20heritage%20while%20safeguarding%20practicality%20and%20modernity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDull%20versus%20vibrant%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20believed%20Indian%20designs%20were%20wanting%20in%20vividness%20and%20creativity%20compared%20to%20athletes%20from%20other%20countries%20who%20wore%20vibrant%20uniforms.%20It%20was%20a%20treat%20to%20watch%20smaller%20nations%20like%20Mongolia%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Haiti's%20contingents%20sail%20down%20the%20River%20Seine%20in%20clothes%20reflecting%20their%20handcrafted%20traditions%20and%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMongolia's%20viral%20uniform%20blended%20tradition%20with%20trendy%20to%20produce%20an%20iconic%20ensemble%20using%20the%20nation's%20blue%2C%20red%20and%20white%20colours.%20Sri%20Lanka's%20white%20garments%20featured%20silk%2C%20handmade%20embroidery%20and%20beadwork%20in%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20royal%20courts%20of%20the%2019th%20century.%20The%20Czech%20Republic%20team%20made%20an%20innovative%20and%20practical%20statement%20with%20stylish%20tie-dye%20coats%20as%20it%20rained%20during%20the%20procession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELowering%20morale%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETahiliani's%20choice%20of%20cotton%20and%20viscose%20crepe%20instead%20of%20silk%20was%20questioned%20by%20many%2C%20including%20celebrities.%20Why%20he%20chose%20digital%20ikat%20prints%20over%20weaves%20and%20embroideries%20to%20highlight%20India's%20rich%20handloom%20and%20handicraft%20traditions%20has%20also%20baffled%20critics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20social%20media%2C%20users%20speculated%20that%20the%20'ugly'%20outfits%20couldn't%20be%20good%20for%20our%20athletes'%20morale%20and%20confidence%20on%20the%20opening%20day%20of%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJwala%20Gutta%2C%20ace%20shuttler%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20to%20comment%20on%20X%3A%20%26quot%3BFirst%20not%20all%20girls%20know%20how%20to%20wear%20a%20sari...why%20didn't%20the%20designer%20use%20this%20common%20sense%20and%20make%20a%20pre-draped%20sari%20(which%20is%20in%20current%20trend).%20After%20not%20much%20of%20thinking.%20The%20garments%20which%20was%20(were)%20made%20for%20the%20Indian%20contingent%20participating%20in%20Olympics%20this%20time%20has%20been%20a%20huge%20disappointment!!%20(Especially%20when%20the%20designer%20was%20announced%20I%20had%20huge%20expectations).%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAfter%20not%20much%20of%20thinking..%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20garments%20which%20was%20made%20for%20the%20Indian%20contingent%20participating%20in%20Olympics%20this%20time%20has%20been%20a%20huge%20disappointment!!%20(Especially%20when%20the%20designer%20was%20announced%20I%20had%20huge%20expectations)%3Cbr%3E%5CnFirst%20not%20all%20girls%20know%20how%20to%20wear%20a%20saree%E2%80%A6why%20didn't%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fb5UjzpvUJQ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fb5UjzpvUJQ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Gutta%20Jwala%20%F0%9F%92%99%20(%40Guttajwala)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGuttajwala%2Fstatus%2F1817442488237662627%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2028%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20blogger%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BHello%20Tarun%20Tahiliani!%20I%20have%20seen%20better%20saris%20sold%20in%20Mumbai%20streets%20for%20Rs.200%20than%20these%20ceremonial%20uniforms%20you've%20'designed'.%26quot%3B%20The%20blogger%20called%20it%20a%20combination%20of%20digital%20prints%2C%20cheap%20polyester%20fabric%20and%20the%20tricolour%20thrown%20together%20without%20any%20imagination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETahiliani%20designed%20the%20look%20in%20association%20with%20'Tasva'%2C%20(a%20collaboration%20between%20Tahiliani%20and%20Aditya%20Birla%20Group).%20In%20a%20statement.%20Tasva%20described%20the%20Olympic%20attire%20as%20a%20fusion%20of%20tradition%20and%20modernity%2C%20inspired%20by%20the%20Indian%20tricolour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefending%20his%20decision%20to%20dress%20female%20athletes%20in%20saris%2C%20Tahiliani%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20Olympic%20committee's%20feedback%20influenced%20the%20choice%2C%20as%20saris%20%26quot%3Bcan%20flatter%20any%20body%20type%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20what%20we%20Indians%20wear%2C%20and%20this%20is%20not%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20couture%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20the%20digital%20print%3F%20Tahiliani%20blamed%20it%20on%20tight%20deadlines.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20only%20three%20weeks%20to%20complete%20the%20task%2C%20and%20weaving%20handlooms%20for%20300%20uniforms%20within%20that%20timeline%20was%20not%20feasible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20has%20also%20been%20accused%20of%20incorporating%20the%20'Tasva'%20logo%20in%20the%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupport%20from%20Fraternity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20fashion%20fraternity%20has%20come%20out%20in%20support%20of%20Tahiliani's%20designs.%20Prasad%20Bidapa%2C%20fashion%20curator%2C%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BIndian%20audiences%20now%20expect%20Ambani-level%20pageantry%20and%20extravagant%20looks%20for%20the%20red%20carpet.%20They%20were%20not%20able%20to%20understand%20the%20Gandhian%20simplicity%20of%20a%20sari%20for%20women%20or%20kurta-pyjama%20for%20men.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBidapa%20adds%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20social%20media%20has%20made%20everyone%20a%20fashion%20expert.%20The%20more%20negative%20the%20comments%20the%20higher%20the%20engagement%20and%20number%20of%20likes.%20Many%20top%20designers%20and%20textile%20experts%20I%20spoke%20to%20also%20appreciated%20the%20designs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20Indian%20Olympic%20contingent%20wore%20the%20design%20of%20a%20well-known%20couturier%2C%20in%20the%20world's%20fashion%20capital%2C%20and%20expectations%20soared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20the%20dress%20code%20for%20the%20event%20had%20been%20the%20regulation%20sari%2C%20salwar%20suits%2C%20suits%2C%20bandhgalas%2C%20turbans%20and%20blazers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20surprised%20that%20the%20fashion%20fraternity%20says%20it%20was%20not%20a%20fashion%20show.%20Do%20the%20members%20of%20the%20fashion%20fraternity%20roam%20around%20in%20pyjamas%20when%20they%20are%20not%20in%20a%20fashion%20show%3F%20Every%20sportsperson%2C%20who%20plays%20at%20the%20world%20level%2C%20is%20bigger%20than%20fashion%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20Jwala%20Gutta%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20do%20sportspersons%20other%20than%20cricketers%20have%20to%20compromise%20on%20their%20looks%20and%20clothes%20to%20make%20them%20look%20like%20they%20are%20hard%20working%3F%20Only%20cricketers%20are%20supposed%20to%20look%20glamorous.%20What%20kind%20of%20theory%20is%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20could%20the%20uniform%20have%20been%20better%3F%20Bidapa%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20have%20suggested%20the%20use%20of%20brighter%20and%20bolder%20prints%20like%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Kalamkari%20or%20Rajasthan's%20block%20prints.%20Both%20these%20processes%20take%20time%20and%20would%20not%20have%20been%20possible%20in%20that%20short%20time%20given%20to%20Tarun%20(Tahiliani).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20Tarun%20Tahiliani%20has%20dressed%20many%20stars%20and%20celebrities%20-%20even%20Kim%20Kardashian%20-%20for%20a%20recent%20Indian%20wedding%20extravaganza.%20He%20put%20minimal%20effort%20into%20the%20costumes%20for%20the%20India%20contingent%2C%20they%20say%20uncharitably.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20local%20designers%20from%20Mongolia%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20managed%20to%20charm%20a%20very%20tough%20crowd%20-%20the%20internet%20fashion%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722940620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fg0i162so_indian-olympic_625x300_28_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fred-carpet-or-not-furious-debate-over-indias-olympics-uniform-6275908%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20contingent's%20attire%20at%20the%20Olympics%20opening%20ceremony%20has%20provoked%20severe%20criticism.%20