arge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elysian%20E-9X%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b1dd7db4912df3ae19179a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Elysian%20E9X%20would%20be%20powered%20by%20batteries%20stored%20within%20its%20wings.%3Cp%3EElysian%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDutch%20startup%20Elysian%20unveiled%20plans%20for%20an%20electric%20plane%20it%20says%20could%20fly%20500%20miles%20on%20a%20single%20charge.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20says%20the%20E9X%20has%20eight%20engines%20and%20folding%20wingtips.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EElectric%20planes%20have%20largely%20failed%20to%20take%20off%2C%20with%20both%20NASA%20and%20Rolls%20Royce%20scrapping%20efforts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20years%20of%20hype%2C%20electric%20planes%20have%20largely%20failed%20to%20get%20off%20the%20ground%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-kittyhawk-google-founder-billionaire-larry-page-flying-car-company-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estartups%20collapsing%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20existing%20prototypes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-planes-future-of-aviation-problems-regulations-2020-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruggling%20to%20take%20off%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElysian%2C%20an%20electric%20plane%20startup%20based%20in%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20thinks%20it%20has%20found%20a%20way%20to%20change%20that%3B%20a%20novel%20new%20battery-powered%20jet%20that%20it%20says%20could%20fly%2090%20passengers%20up%20to%20500%20miles%20on%20a%20single%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPart%20of%20the%20reason%20why%20the%20aerospace%20industry%20has%20been%20so%20skeptical%20about%20large%20electric%20aircraft%20is%20because%20to%20electrify%20a%20contemporary%20plane%2C%20you%20had%20to%20make%20very%20wild%20assumptions%20about%20how%20battery%20technology%20will%20develop%2C%26quot%3B%20Elysian%20co-CEO%20Daniel%20Rosen%20Jacobson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20has%20attempted%20to%20get%20around%20this%20problem%2C%20he%20said%2C%20by%20rethinking%20what%20an%20airplane%20should%20look%20like%20to%20squeeze%20every%20drop%20of%20performance%20from%20current%20battery%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20is%20the%20E9X%20concept%2C%20a%2090-passenger%20electric%20plane%20about%20the%20size%20of%20an%20A320%20that%20could%20be%20capable%20of%20traveling%20up%20to%20500%20miles%20on%20a%20single%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20E9X%20has%20larger%20wings%20and%20a%20slimmer%20body%20than%20most%20conventional%20aircraft%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20in%20place%20of%20two%20to%20four%20jet%20engines%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eit%20has%208%20propellor%20engines%20powered%20by%20batteries%20stored%20inside%20the%20wings%2C%20a%20design%20choice%20that%20aims%20to%20make%20the%20E-9X%20as%20light%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plane%20would%20also%20come%20with%20folding%20wingtips%2C%20which%20Elysian%20says%20are%20intended%20to%20improve%20its%20aerodynamics%20and%20allow%20it%20to%20fit%20within%20gates%20designed%20for%20current%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20E9X%20currently%20exists%20only%20on%20paper%2C%20with%20Elysian%20planning%20to%20build%20a%20full-scale%20prototype%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacobson%20believes%20that%20if%20E9X%20and%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjsx-intends-buy-hybrid-electric-planes-semi-private-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elarge%20short-haul%20electric%20jets%20like%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20become%20a%20reality%2C%20they%20could%20dramatically%20cut%20the%20aviation%20industry's%20CO2%20emissions%20and%20transform%20the%20flying%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20become%20much%20more%20attractive%20to%20use%20aircraft%20versus%20pretty%20much%20any%20oth