20energy%20they%20provide.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20for%20now%2C%20electric%20propulsion%20is%20only%20viable%20for%20small%20aircraft%20with%20a%20limited%20range%2C%26quot%3B%20Sophie%20Armanini%2C%20a%20lecturer%20in%20Aerial%20%3Cspan%3ERobotics%3C%2Fspan%3E%20at%20Imperial%20College%20London%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.eu%2Farticle%2Felectric-aircraft-emissions-aviation-pipistrel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Politico%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElysian%20believes%20it%20has%20a%20workaround%20with%20the%20E9X%2C%20but%20Jacobson%20acknowledged%20that%20making%20large%20electric%20planes%20a%20reality%20will%20still%20be%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20E9X%20would%20require%20around%2011%20to%2013%20megawatts%20in%20charging%20capacity%2C%20and%20said%20Elysian%20had%20been%20in%20contact%20with%20one%20energy%20company%20that%20quoted%20a%20price%20of%20under%2010%20million%20euros%20(%2410.9%20million)%20to%20install%20the%20necessary%20charging%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacobson%20believes%20this%20figure%20is%20comparatively%20small%20in%20the%20scale%20of%20airport%20infrastructure%20overhauls%20and%20said%20that%20the%20transformative%20impact%20of%20large%20electric%20planes%20would%20make%20it%20a%20small%20price%20to%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUntil%20now%2C%20the%20industry%20didn't%20think%20there%20was%20a%20commercial%20electric%20solution.%20Now%20with%20this%20concept%20there%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-plane-fly-90-passengers-500-miles-on-single-charge-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722939233000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b1e243393cd3c8629b7c07%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-plane-fly-90-passengers-500