be%20around%20%241%2C400%20to%20%241%2C800%20%E2%80%94%20costs%20that%20have%20only%20risen%20in%20recent%20years.%20The%20median%20rental%20price%20in%20Minneapolis%20sits%20at%20%241%2C495%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zillow.com%2Frental-manager%2Fmarket-trends%2Fminneapolis-mn%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZillow%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeGeros's%20move%20is%20one%20that%20more%20retirees%20are%20contemplating%3A%20Amidst%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-boomer-social-security-pension-move-abroad-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolitical%20unrest%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-x-baby-boomers-savings-cant-afford-retirement-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshaky%20finances%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomer-retirement-social-security-insurance-cancer-diagnosis-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epricey%20healthcare%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20retiring%20in%20the%20US%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20safe%20bet%20for%20some.%20And%20that's%20led%20boomers%20and%20retirees%20like%20LeGeros%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-latin-america-retirement-expensive-social-security-panama-costa-rica-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elook%20elsewhere%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Of%20course%2C%20as%20LeGeros%20notes%2C%20the%20move%20comes%20with%20its%20own%20challenges%2C%20and%20it%20requires%20a%20level%20of%20openness%20and%20cultural%20curiosity%20for%20those%20who%20wish%20to%20thrive.%20But%20financially%2C%20it's%20been%20incredibly%20cost-effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20working%20until%20I%20find%20my%20next%20occupation%20or%20my%20next%2C%20I%20don't%20know%2C%20passion%2C%26quot%3B%20LeGeros%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20live%20off%20of%20the%20money%20I%20have.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ed21e67-7769-4e1c-b417-4cb04bc34b00%5C%22%3EA%20need%20for%20cultural%20appreciation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20LeGeros%2C%20retiring%20abroad%20has%20been%20a%20boon.%20Right%20when%20he%20arrived%2011%20years%20ago%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehe%20found%20that%20his%20cost%20of%20living%20was%2020%25%20of%20what%20it%20had%20been%20in%20the%20US.%20Today%2C%20even%20with%20inflation%2C%20his%20costs%20are%20maybe%2050%25%20of%20what%20they%20would've%20been.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20actually%20eat%20out%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeGeros%20is%20a%20permanent%20resident%20of%20Mexico%20but%20not%20a%20citizen.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHis%20life%20as%20a%20transplant%20is%20content%2C%20but%20he%20said%20that's%20not%20the%20case%20for%20everyone.%20There%20are%20still%20adjustments%20moving%20abroad%2C%20and%20hopeful%20movers%20need%20to%20know%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20should%20not%20only%20think%20about%20the%20dollars%20that%20you'd%20be%20saving%2C%20you%20have%20to%20think%20about%20the%20culture%20you're%20moving%20into%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20recalled%20that%20when%20he%20first%20made%20the%20move%20abroad%2C%20he%20met%20another%20mover%20couple%20with%20a%20booming%20business.%20But%20they%20were%20still%20unhappy%2C%20finding%20the%20cultural%20adjustment%20jarring.%20Ultimately%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20head%20back%20to%20the%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20think%2C%20well%2C%20I'm%20rich%20now.%20I%20can%20live%20in%20a%20country%20that%20I%20pay%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost%20I%20would%20pay%20if%20I%20lived%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20I%20can%20do%20anything%20I%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20that's%20not%20necessarily%20the%20actual%20picture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20abroad%20brings%20its%20own%20challenges%2C%20along%20with%20rewards.%20Learning%20a%20language%20can%20be%20its%20own%20difficulty%2C%20although%20it%20should%20be%20a%20priority%20for%20anyone%20who%20moves%20abroad%2C%20he%20said.%20He's%20still%20learning%20Spanish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeGeros%20said%20that%20negotiating%20simple%20things%20%E2%80%94%20like%20healthcare%20and%20everyday%20social%20interactions%20%E2%80%94%20can%20present%20its%20own%20hurdles.%20Norms%20around%20driving%20or%20when%20to%20show%20up%20for%20events%20can%20also%20present%20new%20challenges.%20He%20said%20driving%20is%20much%20more%20lax%20in%20Mexico%2C%20and%2C%20as%20a%20cyclist%20in%20the%20country%2C%20he%20got%20hit%20by%20a%20car%20once%20and%20nearly%20lost%20his%20right%20leg.%20Those%20are%20just%20a%20few%20of%20the%20challenges%20and%20adjustments%20that%20he's%20faced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20things%20I%20would%20suggest%20people%20do%20when%20they%20come%20down%20is%20to%20find%20a%20community%20and%20identify%20with%20a%20community%20of%20foreigners%2C%20not%20necessarily%20Americans%2C%20but%20foreigners.%20And%20that%20could%20be%20a%20church%2C%20it%20could%20be%20a%20cause%20like%20pets%20or%20stray%20dogs%20or%20stray%20cats%2C%20whatever%2C%26quot%3B%20LeGeros%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20just%20always%20have%20a%20support%20group%20that%20are%20dealing%20with%20living%20abroad%20because%20you%20need%20that%20adjustment%20group%20to%20help%20you%20put%20things%20into%20perspective.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20moving%20isn't%20just%20as%20easy%20as%20picking%20up%20and%20heading%20out%20one%20day.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretire-abroad-international-retirement-save-advice-tips-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPotential%20retirement%20movers%3C%2Fa%3E%20need%20to%20get%20their%20finances%20squared%20away%2C%20learn%20about%20a%20slew%20of%20residency%20requirements%2C%20adapt%20to%20new%20taxation%20systems%2C%20and%20deal%20with%20a%20whole%20new%20(although%20often%20cheaper)%20healthcare%20system.%20For%20some%20would-be%20retirees%2C%20all%20of%20that%