ting%20partner%20of%20the%202028%20Los%20Angeles%20Olympics%2C%20in%20a%20major%20boost%20for%20the%20Games'%20goal%20of%20%242.5%20billion%20in%20domestic%20sponsorship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAutodesk%20was%20named%20the%20%26quot%3Bofficial%20design%20and%20make%20platform%20of%20the%20LA28%20Olympics%20and%20Paralympic%20Games%20and%20Team%20USA%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20announced%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20first%20time%20the%20business-to-business%20tech%20company%20has%20sponsored%20the%20Olympics%20and%20follows%20a%20spree%20of%20major%20marketing%20activations%2C%20including%20an%20ad%20campaign%20during%20the%20Oscars%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fautodesk-cmo-las-vegas-sphere-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etakeover%20of%20the%20Sphere%20in%20Las%20Vegas%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAutodesk's%20software%20will%20be%20used%20to%20help%20adapt%20more%20than%2040%20existing%20venues%20across%20southern%20California%20%3Cspan%3Eand%20design%20temporary%20buildings%20to%20support%20LA28's%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Folympics.com%2Fioc%2Fnews%2Fla28-updates-venue-masterplan-with-world-class-stadiums-and-arenas-chosen-to-enhance-athlete-and-fan-experience%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eno-new-permanent-venues%20plan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELA28%20also%20intends%20to%20use%20Autodesk%20software%20to%20design%20transport%20and%20traffic%20control%20plans%20to%20be%20used%20in%20the%20city%20throughout%20the%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDara%20Treseder%2C%20Autodesk's%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20sponsorship%20was%20helping%20drive%20new%20business%20for%20the%20company%20as%20it%20works%20on%20LA's%20%241%20billion%20temporary%20overlay%20and%20construction%20plan.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20the%20partnership%20should%20also%20help%20elevate%20Autodesk's%20brand%20through%20a%20legacy%20of%20%26quot%3Bleaving%20the%20city%20better%20than%20we%20found%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20business%20case%20wrote%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20Treseder%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222745%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dara%20Treseder%20Autodesk%20CMO%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b1e227a5247369a3e9ab38%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222059%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAutodesk%20Chief%20Marketing%20Officer%20Dara%20Treseder%20told%20BI%20the%20business%20case%20for%20sponsoring%20the%20Gamess%20'wrote%20itself.'%3Cp%3EAutodesk%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAutodesk%20intends%20to%20air%20a%2030-second%20TV%20spot%20during%20the%20hand-off%20section%20of%20the%20Paris%20Olympics'%20closing%20ceremony%20on%20August%2011%20highlighting%20the%20sponsorship%2C%20as%20well%20as%20social%20media%20ads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20LA%20Olympics%20is%20estimated%20to%20cost%20%247%20billion%2C%20which%20organizers%20have%20said%20they%20hope%20to%20offset%20with%20sponsorships%2C%20ticket%20sales%2C%20media%20rights%2C%20and%20other%20revenue.%20In%20June%2C%20the%20organizing%20committee%20said%20it%20was%20prioritizing%20retrofitting%20existing%20venues%20rather%20than%20building%20new%20ones%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Folympics.com%2Fioc%2Fnews%2Fla28-updates-venue-masterplan-with-world-class-stadiums-and-arenas-chosen-to-enhance-athlete-and-fan-experience%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebring%20down%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELA28%20has%20faced%20challenges%20in%20reaching%20its%20%242.5%20billion%20domestic%20sponsorship%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20Salesforce%2C%20LA28%2C%20and%20Team%20USA%20%26quot%3Bamicably%20decided%26quot%3B%20to%20end%20their%20seven-year%20deal%2C%20which%20had%20been%20signed%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalesforce's%20exit%20left%20behind%20just%20two%20top-tier%20%26quot%3Bfounding%20partners%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20highest%20paying%20category%20%E2%80%94%20Delta%20Air%20Lines%20and%20Comcast.%20Autodesk%20is%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bofficial%20supporters%26quot%3B%20category%2C%20the%20third%20tier%2C%20joining%20Guild%2C%20Hershey%2C%20and%20Dick's%20Sporting%20Goods.%20The%20International%20Organizing%20Committee%20will%20also%20share%20with%20LA28%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20proceeds%20of%20its%20worldwide%20sponsorship%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChristopher%20Pepe%2C%20LA28%20chief%20commercial%20officer%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20the%20LA%20Games%20had%20achieved%20north%20of%20%241%20billion%20in%20sponsorship%20commitments%20and%20is%20already%20ahead%20of%20what%20the%20Paris%202024%20Olympics%20has%20achieved%2C%20with%20four%20years%20to%20go%20before%20the%20event.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20published%20by%20Ampere%20Analysis%20last%20month%20suggested%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ampereanalysis.com%2Finsight%2Fparis-olympics-sees-a-60-uplift-in-sponsorship-revenue%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNew%2520research%2520from%2520Ampere%2520Analysis%2CTokyo%2520Olympic%2520Games%2520of%25202020.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParis%20was%20on%20track%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20reach%20its%20%241.34%20billion%20domestic%20sponsorship%20revenue%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20are%20looking%20for%20hundreds%20of%20brands%20to%20be%20announced%20along%20the%20way%3B%20we%20need%20to%20look%20at%20a%20smaller%20number%20of%20brands%2C%20quality%20brands%20at%20the%20top%20of%20their%20category%2C%20to%20help%20us%20innovate%2C%26quot%3B%20Pepe%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20price%20tag%20is%20probably%20larger%20than%20some%20Games%20because%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlex%20Balfour%2C%20cofounder%20of%20the%20marketing%20agency%20Generate%20Digital%20and%20former%20head%20of%20media%20for%20the%20London%202012%20Olympics%2C%20said%20LA28%20faced%20high%20expectations%20for%20sponsorship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20this%20was%20partl