%20of%2086.48m%2C%20setting%20a%20new%20under-20%20world%20record%2C%20drawing%20global%20attention%20to%20his%20talent.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20his%20breakthrough%20came%20in%202017%20when%20he%20claimed%20gold%20at%20the%20Asian%20Athletics%20Championship.%20Later%2C%20he%20also%20won%20gold%20at%20the%202018%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20win%20the%20javelin%20throw%20at%20the%20event%2C%20as%20well%20as%20at%20the%20Jakarta%202018%20Asian%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20journey%20to%20becoming%20a%20sports%20star%2C%20Neeraj%20has%20trained%20under%20Australian%20coach%20Garry%20Calvert%20at%20the%20Olympic%20Training%20Centre.%20Despite%20overcoming%20numerous%20obstacles%20to%20achieve%20top-tier%20status%2C%20Neeraj%20credits%20his%20success%20to%20this%20comprehensive%20support%20system.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CGarry%20sir%20has%20been%20a%20huge%20source%20of%20knowledge%20and%20help%E2%80%A6%20and%20my%20parents%20have%20always%20backed%20me%20to%20push%20myself%20to%20be%20the%20best%20in%20whatever%20it%20is%20that%20I%20do.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2026%2C%20Neeraj%20is%20a%20leading%20javelin%20thrower.%20As%20the%20current%20Olympic%2C%20World%2C%20and%20Asian%20Games%20javelin%20champion%2C%20he%20made%20history%20as%20the%20first%20Asian%20to%20win%20an%20Olympic%20gold%20in%20javelin%20at%202020%20Tokyo%20Olympics%20%E2%80%94%20joining%20Abhinav%20Bindra%20as%20one%20of%20just%20two%20Indians%20to%20achieve%20individual%20Olympic%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Neeraj%20has%20added%20gold%20medals%20from%20the%202022%20Diamond%20League%2C%20the%202022%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20and%20the%202023%20World%20Championships%20in%20Budapest%20to%20his%20collection.%20The%20victory%20at%20Budapest%20made%20him%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20world%20champion%20in%20any%20athletics%20discipline.%20He%20also%20made%20history%20as%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20win%20at%20the%20World%20Under-20%20Championships%2C%20establishing%20himself%20as%20one%20of%20the%20all-time%20great%20javelin%20throwers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20accolades%20continued%20with%20the%20Arjuna%20Award%20in%202018%2C%20the%20Vishist%20Seva%20Medal%20(VSM)%20in%202020%2C%20the%20Major%20Dhyan%20Chand%20Khel%20Ratna%20Award%20(India%E2%80%99s%20highest%20sporting%20honour)%20in%202021%2C%20the%20Param%20Vishisht%20Seva%20Medal%20(PVSM)%20in%202022%2C%20and%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20(India%E2%80%99s%20fourth%20highest%20civilian%20honour)%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeraj%E2%80%99s%20consistent%20wins%20on%20the%20grandest%20stages%20have%20established%20him%20as%20a%20top-tier%20javelin%20thrower.%20His%20drive%20to%20improve%20his%20throwing%20distances%20has%20garnered%20him%20a%20massive%20social%20media%20following%2C%20exceeding%20nine%20million%20Instagram%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20self-belief%2C%20the%20javelin%20star%20said%20in%20an%20interview%2C%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%20I%20have%20felt%20that%20my%20throw%20has%20not%20been%20up%20to%20the%20mark%2C%20until%20the%20last%20throw.%20But%20I%20still%20believe%20in%20myself%20that%20I%20have%20to%20do%20it%20till%20the%20end.%20And%20in%20many%20competitions%2C%20my%20last%20throw%20has%20been%20the%20best%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fneeraj____chopra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40neeraj____chopra%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722938350000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359918%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Neeraj%20Chopra%2C%20hailing%20from%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Khandra%20village%2C%20began%20his%20athletic%20journey%20after%20a%20chance%20encounter%20with%20javelin%20throw.%20Despite%20financial%20challenges%2C%20his%20dedication%20a