've%20provided%20developer%20support%2C%20account%20management%2C%20and%20consulting%2C%20and%20I%20currently%20support%20Azure%20Identity%2C%20a%20Microsoft%20cloud%20service%20provider.%20Working%20in%20tech%2C%20it's%20tough%20to%20disconnect%20from%20technology%2C%20and%20as%20a%20father%20of%20four%2C%20I%20can't%20imagine%20how%20tough%20it%20is%20for%20my%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20work%20in%20tech%2C%20I'm%20not%20very%20familiar%20with%20social%20media.%20Before%20my%20children%20hit%20puberty%2C%20it%20never%20dawned%20on%20me%20that%20technology%20could%20be%20an%20evil%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20my%20kids%20are%209%2C%2012%2C%2013%2C%20and%2015%2C%20and%20I'm%20worried%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmagali-berdah-14-thrown-prison-cyberbullying-french-influencer-keyboard-warriors-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecyberbullying%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20catfishing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20taken%20steps%20to%20manage%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparenting-screen-time-not-worried-about-what-experts-say-effects-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escreen%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20access%20to%20apps%2C%20even%20though%20I%20feel%20guilty%20about%20doing%20so%20sometimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20parent%2C%20I%20am%20responsible%20for%20guiding%20my%20children%20and%20showing%20I%20can%20disconnect%20from%20screens%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cbb5a183-2ac7-49ee-b2fc-d673afdf2dc2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20kids%20are%20on%20their%20screens%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20so%20am%20I%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconfessions-of-a-screen-addict-introduction-to-the-your-brain-on-apps-series-2018-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaddicted%20to%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'll%20spend%20hours%20reading%20through%20tech%20documents%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20latest%20developments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spend%20around%2012%20hours%20a%20day%20working%20at%20my%20computer.%20I%20also%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-facebook-apps-used-half-world-population-earnings-mark-zuckerberg-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Instagram%20a%20little%20bit%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20often%20on%20my%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20kids%20were%20young%2C%20I%20noticed%20their%20grandmother%20wanted%20them%20to%20have%20a%20tablet%20if%20she%20watched%20them%20as%20a%20distraction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20like%20giving%20them%20a%20device%20to%20keep%20them%20occupied.%20I've%20tried%20to%20talk%20to%20my%20kids%20in%20the%20car%20instead%20of%20letting%20them%20be%20on%20tablets%2C%20but%20as%20a%20society%2C%20we%20expose%20our%20kids%20to%20lots%20of%20technology.%20I've%20sometimes%20even%20asked%20them%20to%20watch%20TV%20while%20I%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20three%20oldest%20kids%20have%20iPads%20provided%20by%20their%20school%2C%20and%20they%20also%20have%20personal%20Android%20tablets%20and%20phones.%20My%20youngest%20has%20a%20phone%20but%20can't%20make%20calls.%20He%20uses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fftc-meta-misled-parents-violated-privacy-facebook-messenger-kids-app-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMessenger%20Kids%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20can%20control%20who%20he%20talks%20to.%20My%20oldest%20has%20a%20desktop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%2012-year-old%20is%20smart%20and%20does%20well%20in%20school%2C%20so%20he%20gets%20bored%20easily.%20He%20used%20to%20come%20home%20from%20school%20and%20just%20sit%20on%20his%20phone.%20He'd%20easily%20be%20on%20it%20for%2020%20hours%20or%20play%20a%20video%20game%20for%2016%20hours%20straight%2C%20which%20flabbergasted%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I've%20tried%20to%20talk%20to%20my%20kids%20about%20consuming%20technology%20in%20moderation%2C%20they%20comment%20that%20I'm%20on%20my%20screen%20all