change%20that%20and%20says%20she's%20confident%20attitudes%20are%20shifting.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Sophie%20Morgan%2C%20an%20NBC%20and%20Channel%204%20presenter%20and%20travel%20writer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3EIt%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20TV%20presenter%2C%20travel%20writer%2C%20and%20disability%20advocate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20in%20a%20car%20crash%20when%20I%20was%2018%20years%20old%20that%20left%20me%20paralyzed%20from%20the%20chest%20down.%20I've%20been%20a%20wheelchair%20user%20for%2021%20years%20this%20summer%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20my%20job%20as%20a%20TV%20host%2C%20I've%20flown%20all%20over%20the%20world.%20I%20love%20nothing%20more%20than%20to%20travel%2C%20but%20as%20a%20disabled%20person%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famid-airline-chaos-wheelchair-users-are-the-latest-casualties-delays-cancellations%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflying%20often%20feels%20like%20a%20lottery%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20you%20never%20really%20know%20what%20you're%20going%20to%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20time%20I%20fly%2C%20I%20dread%20it.%20Because%20of%20my%20disability%2C%20I%20always%20starve%20and%20dehydrate%20beforehand%20because%20I%20often%20can't%20independently%20use%20the%20bathroom%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20survey%20from%20disability%20equality%20charity%20Scope%20found%20that%20one%20in%20four%20people%20who%20use%20a%20mobility%20aid%20say%20it%20has%20been%20lost%20or%20damaged%20while%20flying%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20wheelchair%20users%20like%20me%2C%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-blogger-carried-off-air-canada-operated-flight-wheelchair-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewheelchair%20getting%20broken%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20just%20an%20inconvenience%20like%20having%20your%20luggage%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20of%20flying%20has%2C%20at%20times%2C%20been%20so%20horrendous%20that%20I've%20asked%20myself%2C%20why%20am%20I%20flying%3F%20It's%20like%20returning%20to%20an%20abusive%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22549f0f11-4459-4890-ac16-89427e55a2ca%5C%22%3ECampaigning%20for%20change%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202023%2C%20I%20took%20a%20British%20Airways%20flight%20from%20the%20United%20States%20to%20Heathrow%2C%20London.%20My%20wheelchair%20had%20been%20transported%20in%20the%20hold%20in%20two%20separate%20pieces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20reason%2C%20somebody%20had%20decided%20to%20reattach%20them%20without%20knowing%20what%20to%20do%20and%20did%20so%20incorrectly.%20The%20chair%20broke%2C%20leaving%20the%20frame%20buckled%20and%20the%20attachment%20broken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BWhen%20contacted%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20British%20Airways%20apologized%20for%20Sophie%20Morgan's%20experience%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20extremely%20disheartening%20when%20things%20go%20wrong%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20underestimate%20the%20impact%20this%20has.%20We're%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20we%20deliver%20a%20consistently%20good%20service%2C%20and%20we'll%20be%20working%20closely%20with%20Sophie%20and%20our%20dedicated%20accessibility%20teams%20to%20discuss%20how%20we%20can%20continue%20to%20make%20improvements%20to%20ensure%20a%20great%20flying%20experience%20for%20everyone.%26quot%3B%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20year%2C%20the%20same%20thing%20happened%20twice%20more%20on%20different%20airlines%20at%20different%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20very%2C%20very%20frustrating.%20For%20wheelchair%20users%20like%20me%2C%20our%20wheelchairs%20are%20our%20legs.%20Your%20wheelchair%20being%20broken%20means%20you%20can't%20leave%20the%20house%2C%20you%20can't%20move%2C%20you%20can't%20go%20to%20work%2C%20you%20can't%20do%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20fed%20up%20with%20seeing%20this%20destruction%20and%20chaos%20created%20by%20an%20industry%20that%20makes%20accommodations%20for%20all%20sorts%20of%20passengers%20but%20fails%20to%20accommodate%20disabled%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPets%20have%20more%20rights%20on%20flights%20than%20disabled%20people.%20So%20I%20thought%20enough%20is%20enough%20and%20decided%20to%20start%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frightsonflights.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERights%20on%20Flights%3C%2Fa%3E%20campaign%20to%20try%20to%20raise%20awareness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20core%20of%20the%20campaign%20is%20improving%20the%20rights%20of%20all%20disabled%20flyers%20when%20we%20fly.%20We%20want%20to%20change%20the%20experience%20for%20every%20passenger%20who%20flies%20with%20a%20disability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fbc6814c-f8ec-41fb-8016-7cc4a8e7b058%5C%22%3EAn%20open%20secret%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20co-produced%20a%20documentary%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.channel4.com%2Fprogrammes%2Fsophie-morgans-fight-to-fly%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Fight%20to%20Fly%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Hello%20Sunshine%2C%20the%20production%20company%20set%20up%20by%20Reese%20Witherspoon.%20In%20it%2C%20we%20organized%20three%20groups%20of%20disabled%20passengers%20to%20travel%20undercover%20at%20different%20times%20to%20different%20airports%20on%20the%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20were%20chaos%20and%20confirmed%20what%20we%2C%20as%20the%20disabled%20community%2C%20know%20is%20happening%20all%20the%20time.%20This%20isn't%20news%20to%20us%2C%20but%20to%20everybody%20else%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20a%20secret%20they%20haven't%20been%20let%20in%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20an%20optimist%20and%20believe%20in%20the%20future%20being%20more%20accessible.%20I%20also%20know%20now%2C%20having%20worked%20in%20this%20space%20for%20nearly%20two%20years%2C%20that%20there%20are%20people%20within%20the%20industry%20who%20are%20calling%20out%20for%20it%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20talked%20enough%20now%20about%20the%20spending%20power%20of%20disabled%20people%20for%20airlines%20to%20recognize%20there's%20a%20financial%20gain%20for%20being%20more%20inclusive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20businesses%2C%20especially%20those%20with%20disabled%20employees%20who%20have%20to%20fly%20as%20part%20of%20their%20work%2C%20have%20a%20big%20role%20to%20play%20in%20this%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20the%20power%20to%20tell%20the%20airline%20industry%20to%20get%20its%20act%20together%20and%20hopefully%20get%20them%20to%20change%20things%20for%20the%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-dread-flying-pets-treated-better-planes-than-disabled-people-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722935479000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b0ac86393cd3c8629b3f12%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-dread-flying-pets-treated-better-planes-than-disabled-people-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TV%20host%20Sophie%20Morgan%20told%20Business%20Insider%20flying%20is%20often%20a%20horrific%20experience%20for%20passengers%20with%20disabilities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tcarter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Carter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-dread-flying-pets-treated-better-planes-than-disabled-people-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amazon%20Great%20Freedom%20Festival%20sale%3A%20Check%20deals%20on%20iPhones%2C%20foldables%2C%20more%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722935227000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-07%2F17%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1721215375-6811.JP