ble%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hasina%20resigned%20and%20fled%20Bangladesh%20amid%20deadly%20protests%20yesterday%20as%20the%20country's%20military%20took%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20her%20claim%20that%20many%20foreigners%20had%20their%20eyes%20on%20Bangladesh%2C%20she%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLike%20East%20Timor...they%20will%20carve%20out%20a%20Christian%20country%2C%20taking%20parts%20of%20Bangladesh%20(Chattogram)%20and%20Myanmar%20with%20a%20base%20in%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20had%20vowed%20not%20to%20bow%20down%20to%20any%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20saw%20one%20of%20its%20deadliest%20demonstrations%20on%20Sunday%20with%20over%20100%20protesters%20dying%20in%20clashes%20with%20cops.%20The%20total%20deaths%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20protests%20have%20crossed%20400.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protesters%20breached%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20residence%20on%20Monday%2C%20but%20Ms%20Hasina%20avoided%20a%20direct%20confrontation%2C%20having%20already%20resigned%20and%20fled%20the%20country%20in%20a%20military%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country's%20army%20chief%20called%20a%20press%20conference%20hours%20later%20and%20declared%20an%20interim%20government%20would%20be%20formed%20to%20run%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Ms%20Hasina%20landed%20at%20the%20Hindon%20Air%20Force%20base%20in%20India%20-%20about%2030%20km%20from%20capital%20Delhi.%20She%20is%20likely%20to%20leave%20for%20London%20where%20she%20may%20seek%20asylum%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722930960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fqd5o8k6g_sheikh-hasina_625x300_05_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmonths-before-ouster-sheikh-hasina-had-made-this-explosive-allegation-6274497%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Months%20before%20her%20tragic%20fall%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20had%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3Bconspiracies%26quot%3B%20were%20being%20hatched%20to%20topple%20her%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmonths-before-ouster-sheikh-hasina-had-made-this-explosive-allegation-6274497%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Pak%20Question%20At%20Meeting%20On%20Bangladesh%2C%20S%20Jaishankar's%20Reply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20fielded%20three%20key%20questions%20to%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20during%20the%20all-party%20meeting%20on%20the%20situation%20in%20Bangladesh%20after%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20ouster%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20amid%20violent%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20asked%20what%20is%20the%20government's%20short-term%20and%20long-term%20strategy%20in%20dealing%20with%20diplomatic%20ramifications%20of%20the%20power%20shift%20in%20Dhaka%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%20The%20minister%20replied%20that%20it%20is%20a%20developing%20situation%20and%20the%20Centre%20is%20analysing%20it%20closely%20so%20that%20it%20can%20fine-tune%20its%20next%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20also%20asked%20if%20there%20could%20be%20an%20involvement%20of%20foreign%20powers%2C%20specifically%20Pakistan%2C%20in%20the%20dramatic%20developments%20in%20Dhaka%20over%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%20that%20culminated%20in%20Hasina's%20ouster%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%20The%20Centre%20replied%20that%20it%20is%20investigating%20this%20angle.%20A%20source%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20government%20had%20said%20that%20a%20Pakistan%20diplomat%20had%20been%20constantly%20changing%20his%20social%20media%20display%20picture%20to%20reflect%20the%20situation%20in%20Bangladesh%20amid%20violent%20protests.%20The%20Centre%20said%20is%20probin