3-864x1536.jpeg%20864w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fphiloo-min-1718718943-150x267.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353308%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221599%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPhilo%20turned%20into%20an%20entrepreneur%20in%20her%2060s.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhilo%E2%80%99s%20husband%2C%20KJ%20Thomas%2C%20had%20one%20last%20wish%20that%20his%20wife%20should%20run%20a%20pickle%20business%20and%20make%20a%20name%20for%20herself.%20Over%20the%20past%20six%20years%2C%20the%20Alappuzha%20resident%20has%20built%20%E2%80%98Philo%E2%80%99s%20Pickles%E2%80%99%20from%20her%20house%20with%20the%20help%20of%20her%20daughter-in-law%2C%20Tincy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelatives%20always%20used%20to%20make%20a%20beeline%20for%20her%20pickles%2C%20and%20never%20returned%20without%20a%20jar.%20After%20Thomas%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20Philo%20secured%20a%20food%20licence%20and%20started%20her%20venture%20in%20earnest.%20The%20USP%20of%20these%20pickles%20is%20Philo%E2%80%99s%20recipes%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20are%20made%20at%20home%2C%20in%20small%20batches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20sells%20prawns%E2%80%99%2C%20fish%2C%20meat%20pickles%2C%20dried%20beef%20powder%2C%20chemmeen%20chammanthi%20podi%20(dried%20prawn%20powder)%20and%20seasonal%20vegetable%20pickles%20like%20mango%20and%20sweet%20lime.%20All%20the%20pickles%20are%20made%20in%20small%20batches%20of%2010%20kg%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20spend%20our%20entire%20lives%20buried%20in%20responsibilities.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353263%2Fphilos-pickles-kerala-delivery-india-how-to-start-a-homemade-pickle-business-tips-tincy-thomas%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAs%20we%20cross%2060%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20feel%20bored%20and%20tired%20and%20feel%20that%20we%20aren%E2%80%99t%20capable%20of%20anything