20coffee%20table!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Snehal%20Ambekar%20was%20just%2017%2C%20she%20faced%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295026%2Fhealthcare-startup-to-manage-pcos-for-indian-women-by-sisters-raises-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultitude%20of%20health%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20felt%20dizzy%20when%20she%20stood%20up%2C%20had%20blackouts%2C%20brain%20fog%2C%20sleep%20arthritis%2C%20and%20an%20overwhelming%20sense%20of%20fatigue.%20Things%20were%20so%20bad%20that%20this%20young%20girl%20was%20bedridden.%20She%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20focus%20on%20her%20studies%20or%20even%20step%20out%20of%20the%20house.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20during%20the%20advent%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20and%20since%20some%20of%20her%20symptoms%20matched%20with%20COVID-19%2C%20her%20parents%20had%20her%20tested%20for%20it.%20When%20she%20tested%20negative%2C%20the%20doctor%20suggested%20a%20complete%20blood%20checkup%20with%20tests%20%E2%80%94%20including%20thyroid%2C%20diabetes%2C%20iron%2C%20serum%20creatinine%2C%20Vitamin%20B12%2C%20D%2C%20B9%2C%20etc.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20some%20X-rays%20and%20the%20result%20was%20clear%3A%20Snehal%20was%20nutritionally%20deficient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teenager%20was%20shocked.%20%E2%80%9CI%20ate%20home-cooked%20vegetarian%20meals%20and%20followed%20a%20healthy%20diet.%20I%20was%20young%2C%20healthy%2C%20and%20exercised%20regularly.%20How%20could%20I%20have%20a%20vitamin%20deficiency%3F%20I%20was%20in%20disbelief%2C%E2%80%9D%20Snehal%20recalls%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20diagnosis%20shed%20light%20on%20an%20often-overlooked%20aspect%20of%20nutrition%3A%20the%20potential%20for%20deficiency%20even%20in%20seemingly%20healthy%20diets.%20Moreover%2C%20her%20condition%20was%20compounded%20by%20a%20diagnosis%20of%20Polycystic%20Ovary%20Syn