0Karanwal%2C%20has%20been%20empowering%20young%20rural%20girls%20by%20fostering%20leadership%20through%20local%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20army%20of%20young%20girls%20taking%20leadership%20roles%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%202019-batch%20IAS%20officer%2C%20Minal%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20(CEO)%20at%20the%20Nanded%20Zilla%20Parishad%20of%20Maharashtra%20last%20year.%20During%20a%20training%20session%20organised%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Panchayati%20Raj%20at%20IIM%20Ahmedabad%2C%20she%20learned%20about%20the%20Balika%20Panchayat%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20programme%20was%20efficiently%20run%20by%20a%20village%20sarpanch%20in%20Kutch.%20I%20saw%20one%20of%20the%20members%20of%20this%20panchayat%20talking%20to%20the%20then%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20about%20the%20developments%20in%20her%20village.%20I%20was%20so%20inspired%20to%20see%20the%20confidence%20in%20that%20girl%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspired%20to%20reflect%20this%20pioneering%20approach%20in%20her%20district%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20launched%20it%20in%20February%202024.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wished%20to%20mobilise%20the%20youth%20for%20their%20awareness%20and%20get%20them%20into%20the%20democratic%20understanding%20of%20how%20things%20work%20in%20a%20system%20as%20well%20as%20prepare%20potential%20voters%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-1-1722331421.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20programme%2C%20spearheaded%20by%20IAS%20Minal%20Karanwal%2C%20has%20been%20empowering%20young%20rural%20girls%20by%20fostering%20leadership.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C