t%2C%20who%20understand%20how%20important%20it%20is%20to%20build%20a%20human%20resource%20and%20thereby%20future%20leaders%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20motivate%20other%20gram%20panchayats%2C%20Nanded%20district%20administration%20has%20also%20awarded%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F139481%2Fsundarbans-digambarpur-best-gram-panchayat-bengal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egram%20panchayats%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%93%20Yerdi%2C%20Sawargaon%20Mal%2C%20and%20Amgavhan%20%E2%80%93%20for%20efficiently%20running%20the%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahadevi%2C%20who%20now%20talks%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20gender%20equality%20in%20the%20society%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20want%20to%20feel%20that%20we%20lag%20behind%20anyone%2C%20especially%20in%20a%20country%20where%20the%20president%2C%20finance%20minister%2C%20our%20sarpanch%2C%20and%20CEO%20are%20women.%20We%20do%20not%20feel%20any%20less.%20I%20aspire%20to%20become%20a%20sarpanch%20and%20lead%20my%20village%20one%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeing%20the%20success%20of%20the%20first%20phase%2C%20Minal%20has%20recently%20launched%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20the%20project%20in%20June.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20second%20leg%20of%20Balika%20Panchayat%20focuses%20on%20suggesting%20resolutions%20for%20gram%20panchayats.%20Our%20next%20goal%20is%20to%20see%20how%20these%20girls%20start%20giving%20resolutions%20with%20unanimity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPersonally%2C%20this%20initiative%20has%20been%20immensely%20satisfying%20for%20Minal.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20initiative%20has%20been%20very%20fulfilling%20as%20it%20is%20apart%20from%20my%20routine%20work.%20If%20we%20could%20implement%20an%20idea%20on%20the%20grassroots%20where%20young%20rural%20girls%20feel%20confident%20and%20empowered%20in%20taking%20leadership%20roles%20in%20the%20male-dominated%20society%2C%20then%20we%20have%20already%20started%20achieving%20transformation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Minal%20Karanwal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722498878000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-2_11zon-1722331557.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359001%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IAS%20Minal%20Karanwal%2C%20chief%20executive%20officer%20of%20Nanded%20Zila%20Parishad%2C%20has%20introduced%20the%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%98Balika%20Panchayat%E2%80%99%20in%20Nanded%20district%20of%20Maharashtra.%20It%20helps%20young%20girls%20become%20active%20citizens%20who%20are%20able%20to%20target%20and%20address%20local%20issues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359001%2Fias-officer-balika-panchayat-nanded-maharashtra-young-girls-fight-alcoholism-child-marriage%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98We%20Were%20Born%20To%20Stand%20Out%E2%80%99%3A%2032%20People%20With%20Autism%20Share%20What%20They%20Need%20the%20World%20to%20Understand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Tanya%20Joseph%20(15)%2C%20who%20identifies%20as%20an%20individual%20with%20non-speaking%20autism%20was%20asked%20if%20she%20could%20change%20anything%20about%20her%20situation%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20flinch%20a%20second%20before%20writing%20down%20her%20response%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20were%20to%20do%20that.%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20Tanya%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAutism%20is%20a%20part%20of%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20continued.%20Tanya%E2%80%99s%20response%20is%20a%20window%20into%20hers%20and%20the%20worlds%20of%2031%20other%20people%20diagnosed%20with%20non-speaking%20autism%2C%20who%20have%20bared%20their%20souls%20in%20the%20book%20%E2%80%98Talking%20Fingers%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20Tanya%E2%80%99s%20view%2C%20they%20believe%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F60615%2Fautism-sai-connections-empowered-mothers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eautism%20is%20not%20something%20to%20be%20wished%20away%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20an%20integral%20piece%20of%20the%20jigsaw%20which%20is%20their%20lives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20perspective%20amazes%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20leading%20up%20to%20this%20piece%20introduced%20me%20to%20the%20spectrum%20of%20non-speaking%20autism%2C%C2%A0referring%20to%20cases%20in%20which%20a%20person%20with%20autism%20has%20a%20delay%20or%20difficulty%20with%20speech.%20As%20statistics%20in%20%3Cem%3EHealthline%20%3C%2Fem%3Esuggest%2C%20around%2025%20to%2030%20percent%20of%20people%20with%20ASD%20(Autism%20Spectrum%20Disorder)%20are%20minimally%20verbal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I%20could%20convey%20the%20essence%20of%20non-speaking%20autism%20to%20you%20through%20research%20findings%2C%20news%20publishings%20and%20heavy%20jargon.%20But%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20do%20it%20justice.%20Instead%2C%20a%20sentence%20I%20read%20in%20an%20article%20published%20by%20the%20Organisation%20for%20Autism%20Research%20does%20the%20trick%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EImagine%20you%20answer%20everyone%20who%20says%20something%20to%20you%2C%20but%20only%20you%20can%20hear%20it.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWritten%20by%20Philip%20Reyes%2C%20an%20individual%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F327878%2Fsejal-shah-mariposa-foundation-shares-lessons-for-raising-a-child-with-disability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enon-speaking%20autism%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20article%20condemns%20the%20popular%20belief%20that%20non-speaking%20equals%20non-thinking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20is%20this%20very%20point%20that%20Padma%20Jyothi%20and%20Chitra%20Paul%20%E2%80%94%20both%20mothers%20to%20children%20with%20non-speaking%20autism%20%E2%80%94%20are%20driving%20home%20through%20their%20books%20Talking%20Fingers%20(2022)%20and%20Talking%20Fingers%20Volume%202%20(2024).%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESee%20their%20world%20for%20what%20it%20is%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESilence%20speaks%20louder%20than%20words.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20compiling%20Talking%20Fingers%2C%20the%20meaning%20of%20this%20adage%20became%20clear%20to%20the%20mother%20duo%2C%20who%20refrain%20from%20calling%20themselves%20authors%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20%3Cem%3Eedited%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20book%3B%20they%20%5Bthe%2032%20individuals%5D%20are%20the%20real%20authors%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20their%20chapters%2C%20the%20books%20attempt%20to%20bust%20myths%20that%20have%20shadowed%20individuals%20with%20autism%20for%20decades.%20And%20this%20is%20done%20through%20a%20unique%20approach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20a%20one-directional%20narrative%2C%20the%20books%20are%20a%20first-hand%20account%20of%20the%20challenges%2C%20hopes%20and%20dreams%20of%20people%20who%20belong%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F315291%2Fhyderabad-neena-rao-started-margika-foundation-for-neurodivergent-autism-care-support%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eneurodivergent%20spectrum%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Artists%2C%20writers%2C%20and%20publishers%2C%20these%2032%20individuals%20may%20have%20non-speaking%20autism%20but%20that%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20hindered%20them%20from%20making%20people%20sit%20up%20and%20take%20note%20of%20their%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20eulogise%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20is%20their%20only%20ask.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20humans%20first%3B%20and%20people%20with%20autism%2C%20second.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20stage%20is%20t